528
00:42:18,036 --> 00:42:19,119
Ma!

529
00:42:54,489 --> 00:42:55,489
Just hold on.

530
00:42:58,701 --> 00:43:01,495
Pinned down, they returned fire.

531
00:43:03,289 --> 00:43:05,999
And finally, the reinforcements arrived.

532
00:43:08,169 --> 00:43:11,672
When it was over,
