566
00:46:37,003 --> 00:46:41,548
Not Brooke. Nobody.
Mom is always going to be with us.

567
00:46:42,383 --> 00:46:43,675
Right here.

568
00:46:45,052 --> 00:46:48,889
Because we remember her
like nothing could ever take her away.

569
00:46:50,057 --> 00:46:54,269
If Brooke and I ever start thinking
about something like that

